flowchart TB
  LOOP[conversation_loop<br/>统一 Agent 主循环]
  BASE[ProviderTransport ABC<br/>convert_messages / convert_tools / build_kwargs / normalize_response]
  CHAT[ChatCompletionsTransport<br/>OpenAI-compatible 路径]
  ANTH[AnthropicTransport<br/>Messages API + cache stats + thinking blocks]
  BEDROCK[BedrockTransport<br/>Converse API]
  CODEX[Codex / Codex app-server<br/>事件投影为 OpenAI 形状]
  NORM[NormalizedResponse<br/>content / tool_calls / usage / provider_data]
  RETRY[Retry/Fallback/Compression<br/>仍由 AIAgent 主循环掌控]

  LOOP --> BASE
  BASE --> CHAT
  BASE --> ANTH
  BASE --> BEDROCK
  BASE --> CODEX
  CHAT --> NORM
  ANTH --> NORM
  BEDROCK --> NORM
  CODEX --> NORM
  NORM --> LOOP
  LOOP --> RETRY

  WHY1[为什么这样设计：<br/>Provider 差异集中在格式转换和响应归一化，<br/>不要把重试、缓存、client 生命周期分散到每个 adapter]
  WHY2[为什么保留 provider_data：<br/>共享字段保持最小，协议特有信息放旁路，<br/>例如 Anthropic thinking blocks / Codex items]
  BASE -.-> WHY1
  NORM -.-> WHY2
